Summary: 2 dark round circles closely together in the sky.
divs: Sighting DetailsWent on the outside to take few photos , 5 in total . In the 1st photo there are these 2 objects & another 2 at much lower altitude & a bit smaller than these so I zoomed on higher ones . In that photo there's also of what appears a dark square but I don't know how to zoom it in on it to show of what this might be , all these seemed to be far away . I just thought MUFON would like to have a look at the attached close up anyway . I've put an approximate time as since the time of sending in my report a wk. ago of a ufo & a projection by the tree , my camera's internal time clock has been messed up by 2 hrs & don't know of how many minutes . As for my hand watch it took over 24 hrs to get back to it's original .
